{"tid":2491740,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(嘈交要自貼身材）健身資訊討論區 107 1001 唔撚開post","createTime":"2021-04-16T13:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T19:22:22.000Z","uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"4774520933ce8e188b45819df7d82f1ad5d10dac","tid":2491740,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:49:21.000Z","msg":"一要努力，二要努力，三四五都係要努力<br />\n<br />\n講咩都得訓練飲食問題心得資料分享<br />\n<br />\n無乜嘢唔好嘈交，因為嘈交要自貼<br />\n唔好貼自己TG出黎，搵食出返去唔會阻你<br />\n<br />\n健身係一條漫長既路,無論增肌定減脂肯堅持就會成功<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------------<br />\n有任何新手問題請睇咗pixel巴既post先<br />\n<br />\n減肥/增磅 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1071429\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1071429</a>"},{"pid":"3adc2f51d1779219377be560d730b4225007bd9e","tid":2491740,"uid":364851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe74bd945f4be2af1008603bb16b562b18c2e1e","tid":2491740,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/crystalball.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ed2b86651c1fd99f1cb6ce795c676d6819ffa9","tid":2491740,"uid":364851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T13:54:36.000Z","msg":"冇人入嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2442eaf3569b1ab7e0a3f5d6f490aa3678f7f5","tid":2491740,"uid":137569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:01:11.000Z","msg":"上個post有清dl搞到椎間突出<br />\n我今日都有啲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0791035d68b1d08066dc8b60896dcfaa679c54a","tid":2491740,"uid":200915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:14:14.000Z","msg":"又Leg Day，自己做Squat唔敢做太重，驚起唔返身<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33bcf15e64edbf641d6b7089