f90d672989161ffb73b9f","tid":2491740,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e24252db17b0e2f03b26537440a155540a408b14","tid":2491740,"uid":62856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:25:38.000Z","msg":"擺低咗成年，近排開始做翻，發覺力不從心<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好sad"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:45:56.000Z","msg":"我都擺低左兩三年啦 都係上個月操返 <br />\n一餅都推到手震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82304ac02774d8008391a293475fa41eeec75ca8","tid":2491740,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0311a96f04a608281f3c58089c4bba5de5513d41","tid":2491740,"uid":121266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T14:35:46.000Z","msg":"有冇巴打試過做gym做到有啲lost<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 基本上係條無盡頭嘅路，又要成日計較啲飲食搞到有時好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T15:46:21.000Z","msg":"係你玩健身 唔係健身玩你"},{"pid":"70a6cbd143a38f64242da7866f6485d976fc59a4","tid":2491740,"uid":7149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:06:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇傷過tfcc過來人？<br />\n1月傷左 冇理 做唔到db 就住咁照做push up <br />\n睇左醫生做左幾次物治都冇好轉<br />\n扭毛巾果d 日常生活全部冇事<br />\n一拎番db 推胸 拉野即痛<br />\n醫生一尾叫抖 點算可以好番哂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />就快想死了 瘦到仆街</blockquote>我覺得最後點都要打針，因為無論我睇物理治療 骨科 照埋MRI X光 佢地不外乎都係叫你：<br />\n<br />\n戴護腕 <br />\n搽藥膏 <br />\n唔好做gym住<br />\n唔好拎重嘢<br />\n<br />\n然後我做哂所有嘢，由10月頭傷咗 抖到2月中 我一發力最後都係會痛 然後就乜柒都做唔到 灰撚到仆街 <br />\n<br />\n去到最尾，我同醫生講 一了百了 打針啦咪撚煩啦 然後打完一次 抖咗around一星期 除非你格硬好大力㩒自己手腕先會有隱約痛 <br />\n<br />\n而家打完針個零2個月，已經冇痛 所以我寧願你唔好哂時間 直接同醫生講打針 <br />\n<br />\n但打針又有分打葡萄糖水 類固醇（我打呢隻）同埋血小板（最貴），要睇你嚴重程度 詳情你問返醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我建議唔好拖 因為實在會令人好撚沮喪 同埋驚你惡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dying.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你果陣係輕定嚴重？<br />\n打prp成2皮..類固醇幾錢到？ 巴打你打咩？？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我呢家正常用手係冇事但一負重即刻唔掂"},{"pid":"75eb9faac2cdaf5b6eb0049d71e8df5cae143133","tid":2491740,"uid":5197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"新手啱啱開始練"},{"pid":"b2063cc5fb4524c5767631ea3dcd418f7d631911","tid":2491740,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:12:14.000Z","msg":"她只是個孩子#14261 搶1001唔開po 立即仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bda4bec08df4bdd08bdd2061ac467f0c0efbbf","tid":2491740,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2063cc5fb4524c5767631ea3dcd418f7d631911","tid":2491740,"uid":158977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:12:14.000Z","msg":"她只是個孩子#14261 搶1001唔開po 立即仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"懂不懂規矩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cee6fbd11f1f35193dfdb081e6ca0f63eb05d29","tid":2491740,"uid":158977,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T16:16:00.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\">🐸🐸🐸🐸🐸🐸🐸🐸🐸<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">Frog ching崇拜區</span>[/size=6]</p><br />\n<br />\n<img